in node selectore you to deploy pod on specific node which is defined in the yml file
You add labels to your nodes, and in your pod you use nodeselectore to choose a node with matchining labels.
nodeSelector is a field of pod spec.
nodeSelector is a simple key value pair


#### When to use nodeselector
- When you want simple scheduling rules.
- When you want to schedule a pod on a specific node.

#### When not to use nodeselector
- When you want to schedule a pod on a node that matches a set of rules.

